snippet.title: Skorecery - PS4 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Skorecery is a mystical local-multiplayer sportslike available NOW on PS4!

Grab your friends and 2-4 controllers to engage in intense couch multiplayer battles. Explore different Spells, Modes and Curses to push your skills to the limits.
